createBridgeAdapter.t.sol
├── when caller does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── when caller has the relevant role
   ├── when the provided bridge controller is not a valid machine instance
   │  └── it should revert with InvalidBridgeController
   └── when the provided bridge controller is a valid machine instance
      ├── when the provided bridge ID is not supported
      │  └── it should revert with InvalidBridgeId
      └── when the provided bridge ID is supported
         ├── it should deploy a bridge adapter instance
         ├── it should emit a BridgeAdapterCreated event
         └── it should register the bridge adapter the provided machine
